    <title>Deleting entities from the toolbar</title>
    <shortdesc>The CWRC-Writer templates come with pre existing entity annotations as example to new
        users. You can easily delete these annotations or any annotations that you don't want in
        your document from the toolbar.</shortdesc>
    <prolog product="CWRC-Writer">
